description.content:
I am a pro-expert in wordpress website development and divi theme customization, development, designing and API integration. I am 7+ years experienced in this field. I have huge happy and satisfied local and global client. I can help to design, customize and develop all device fit wordpress website using Divi theme and plugin.


Common Services:

  • Divi Theme/Plugin customize, install.
  • Build API or integrate third party API.
  • Custom landing page, template design and any others by divi.
  • Speed optimize of divi theme based website.
  • Fix divi website's bugs/errors.
  • Content upload, Slider set up, Blog set up in divi theme.
  • Contact form install, Social media integration.
  • Email Opt-in form.
  • Responsive for all devices, SEO Optimized in divi Wordpress.
  • Payment Gateway Integrations.
  • E-commerce (or Woocommerce) Functionality.
  • User friendly and client's requirement wise website.
  • Create custom functionality or design.


Expertise :

PHP, Wordpress (Woocommerce,Page Builder), Laravel, Javascript, ReactJs, jQuery, Mysql, SQL Server, CSS, Bootstrap.


Have any query? Feel free to inbox me.
